Text: Good luck to you, white_arcades. I'm really only having a little fun with you. Who really cares about all of this? In the end we are both a little retarded. You do sound like a funny guy. You made me laugh. Lots of luck. Cheers!

'Ello mate. You asked for re-seeds of the Papapop series - well, I'm back and seeding again. I work abroad which is why I disappear and re-appear at intervals. You should be good now until beginning of february when I leave for work again.
